---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Contact Us | Web Solution Agency" description="Start your next digital project with Web Solution Agency. Get in touch, tell us about your goals, and let's build something extraordinary together.">
    <!-- Hero -->
    <section x-data="{ loaded: false }" x-init="setTimeout(() => loaded = true, 100)"
             class="relative pt-40 pb-24 overflow-hidden bg-black">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 z-0">
            <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-black via-black/80 to-slate-950 z-10"></div>
            <img src="/images/abstract-wave-bg.png" alt="" class="w-full h-full object-cover opacity-30">
        </div>
        <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-[600px] h-[400px] bg-brand-600/15 blur-[180px] rounded-full pointer-events-none"></div>
        <div class="container mx-auto px-6 relative z-10 text-center"
             x-bind:class="loaded ? 'opacity-100 translate-y-0' : 'opacity-0 translate-y-10'"
             style="transition: all 1s cubic-bezier(0.4, 0, 0.2, 1) 0.2s;">
            <div class="inline-block px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-brand-500/30 bg-brand-500/10 text-brand-400 text-sm font-medium mb-6">
                Contact Us
            </div>
            <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-extrabold text-white leading-[1.1] mb-6 tracking-tight max-w-4xl mx-auto">
                Let's Build Something <span class="text-transparent bg-clip-text bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-400 to-brand-600">Extraordinary.</span>
            </h1>
            <p class="text-xl text-slate-300 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
                Whether you have a detailed brief or just want to discuss your goals — call our Houston-based team directly to explore what's possible.
            </p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Contact Form + Info -->
    <section class="py-24">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-6">
            <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-start">

                <!-- Left: Info -->
                <div>
                    <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-8">How We Work Together</h2>
                    <div class="space-y-6 mb-12">
                        <!-- Step 1 -->
                        <div class="flex gap-5">
                            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-brand-500 text-white font-bold text-sm flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(219,107,39,0.3)]">
                                01
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-1">Discovery Call</h3>
                                <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">We start with a free 30-minute call to understand your goals, challenges, and vision. No pressure, just conversation.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <!-- Step 2 -->
                        <div class="flex gap-5">
                            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-brand-500 text-white font-bold text-sm flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(219,107,39,0.3)]">
                                02
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-1">Proposal & Scope</h3>
                                <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">We send a detailed proposal outlining scope, timeline, and investment — tailored to your specific needs.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <!-- Step 3 -->
                        <div class="flex gap-5">
                            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-brand-500 text-white font-bold text-sm flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(219,107,39,0.3)]">
                                03
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-1">Kickoff & Build</h3>
                                <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">Once aligned, we kick off with a structured sprint-based process, keeping you updated at every milestone.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <!-- Step 4 -->
                        <div class="flex gap-5">
                            <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-brand-500 text-white font-bold text-sm flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 shadow-[0_0_20px_rgba(219,107,39,0.3)]">
                                04
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <h3 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-1">Launch & Beyond</h3>
                                <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed">We launch your project and provide ongoing support, analytics review, and optimization as your partner.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <!-- Contact Details -->
                    <div class="space-y-4 border-t border-white/5 pt-10">
                        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-white mb-6">Get in Touch Directly</h3>
                        <!-- Email -->
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-slate-300">
                            <div class="w-11 h-11 rounded-xl bg-slate-800 flex items-center justify-center text-brand-400 shrink-0">
                                <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 8l7.89 5.26a2 2 0 002.22 0L21 8M5 19h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v10a2 2 0 002 2z"></path></svg>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <div class="text-xs text-slate-500 mb-0.5">Email</div>
                                <div class="text-sm font-medium">websolutiontx@gmail.com</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <!-- Phone -->
                        <div class="flex items-center gap-4 text-slate-300">
                            <div class="w-11 h-11 rounded-xl bg-slate-800 flex items-center justify-center text-brand-400 shrink-0">
                                <svg class="w-5 h-5" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M3 5a2 2 0 012-2h3.28a1 1 0 01.948.684l1.498 4.493a1 1 0 01-.502 1.21l-2.257 1.13a11.042 11.042 0 005.516 5.516l1.13-2.257a1 1 0 011.21-.502l4.493 1.498a1 1 0 01.684.949V19a2 2 0 01-2 2h-1C9.716 21 3 14.284 3 6V5z"></path></svg>
                            </div>
                            <div>
                                <div class="text-xs text-slate-500 mb-0.5">Phone</div>
                                <div class="text-sm font-medium">+1 (832) 266-7209</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- Right: Call Card -->
                <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-900 via-slate-900 to-slate-950 border border-white/10 rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-10 shadow-[0_20px_50px_rgba(219,107,39,0.15)] relative overflow-hidden group">
                    <div class="absolute top-0 right-0 w-80 h-80 bg-brand-500/10 blur-[80px] rounded-full pointer-events-none -z-10 group-hover:bg-brand-500/15 transition-all duration-500"></div>
                    
                    <div class="relative z-10">
                        <div class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-green-500/10 border border-green-500/20 rounded-full px-4 py-1.5 text-xs text-green-400 font-semibold mb-6">
                            <span class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-green-400 animate-pulse"></span>
                            Houston Team Available Now
                        </div>
                        
                        <h2 class="text-2xl font-extrabold text-white mb-4 tracking-tight leading-tight">
                            Connect Instantly with a Growth Expert
                        </h2>
                        
                        <p class="text-slate-300 text-sm leading-relaxed mb-8">
                            Skip the wait times and complex forms. Call us directly to discuss your website design, SEO strategy, AI search optimization, Google Maps presence, or PPC campaigns today.
                        </p>
                        
                        <!-- Premium Call Button -->
                        <a href="tel:+18322667209" class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 w-full py-4 rounded-2xl text-lg font-bold text-white bg-gradient-to-r from-brand-500 to-brand-600 hover:from-brand-600 hover:to-brand-700 transition-all duration-300 shadow-[0_10px_30px_-5px_rgba(219,107,39,0.6)] hover:-translate-y-1 mb-8 border border-brand-400/30 group/btn">
                            <svg class="w-6 h-6 text-white group-hover/btn:animate-bounce" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                                <path d="M20 15.5c-1.2 0-2.4-.2-3.6-.6-.3-.1-.7 0-1 .3l-2.2 2.2c-2.8-1.4-5.1-3.8-6.6-6.6l2.2-2.2c.3-.3.4-.7.2-1-.3-1.1-.5-2.3-.5-3.5 0-.6-.4-1-1-1H4c-.6 0-1 .4-1 1 0 9.4 7.6 17 17 17 .6 0 1-.4 1-1v-3.5c0-.6-.4-1-1-1zM19 12h2c0-4.4-3.6-8-8-8v2c3.3 0 6 2.7 6 6zm-4 0h2c0-2.2-1.8-4-4-4v2c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2z"/>
                            </svg>
                            Call (832) 266-7209
                        </a>
                        
                        <!-- Value highlights -->
                        <div class="space-y-4 border-t border-white/10 pt-8 text-sm">
                            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                                <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-brand-500/10 text-brand-400 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                                    ✓
                                </div>
                                <p class="text-slate-300"><span class="text-white font-semibold">100% Direct:</span> Speak to a live expert in Texas. No automated loops.</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                                <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-brand-500/10 text-brand-400 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                                    ✓
                                </div>
                                <p class="text-slate-300"><span class="text-white font-semibold">Free Auditing:</span> We'll audit your current digital footprint over the phone.</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
                                <div class="w-5 h-5 rounded-full bg-brand-500/10 text-brand-400 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5">
                                    ✓
                                </div>
                                <p class="text-slate-300"><span class="text-white font-semibold">Houston Local:</span> Serving Houston, Austin, Dallas, and beyond.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- FAQ -->
    <section class="py-24 bg-slate-900/50">
        <div class="container mx-auto px-6 max-w-3xl">
            <div class="text-center mb-16">
                <div class="inline-block px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full border border-brand-500/30 bg-brand-500/10 text-brand-400 text-sm font-medium mb-4">
                    FAQ
                </div>
                <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-white">Common Questions</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="space-y-4" x-data="{ open: null }">
                <!-- FAQ 1 -->
                <div class="border border-white/5 rounded-xl overflow-hidden bg-slate-900">
                    <button @click="open = open === 0 ? null : 0"
                            class="w-full flex items-center justify-between p-6 text-left gap-4"
                            id="faq-btn-0">
                        <span class="font-semibold text-white">How long does a typical project take?</span>
                        <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-slate-800 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 transition-transform duration-200"
                               :class="open === 0 ? 'rotate-45 bg-brand-500' : ''">
                            <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M12 4v16m8-8H4"></path></svg>
                        </span>
                    </button>
                    <div x-show="open === 0"
                         x-transition:enter="transition ease-out duration-200"
                         x-transition:enter-start="opacity-0 -translate-y-2"
                         x-transition:enter-end="opacity-100 translate-y-0"
                         class="px-6 pb-6 text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed border-t border-white/5 pt-4" style="display:none;">
                        Project timelines vary based on scope. A standard website takes 4–8 weeks, while complex web apps or mobile projects can take 3–6 months. We always provide a detailed timeline in our proposal.
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- FAQ 2 -->
                <div class="border border-white/5 rounded-xl overflow-hidden bg-slate-900">
                    <button @click="open = open === 1 ? null : 1"
                            class="w-full flex items-center justify-between p-6 text-left gap-4"
                            id="faq-btn-1">
                        <span class="font-semibold text-white">What is your pricing structure?</span>
                        <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-slate-800 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 transition-transform duration-200"
                               :class="open === 1 ? 'rotate-45 bg-brand-500' : ''">
                            <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M12 4v16m8-8H4"></path></svg>
                        </span>
                    </button>
                    <div x-show="open === 1"
                         x-transition:enter="transition ease-out duration-200"
                         x-transition:enter-start="opacity-0 -translate-y-2"
                         x-transition:enter-end="opacity-100 translate-y-0"
                         class="px-6 pb-6 text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed border-t border-white/5 pt-4" style="display:none;">
                        We work on project-based pricing tailored to your scope. After our discovery call, we send a detailed quote. Projects typically range from $5k for small sites to $50k+ for enterprise solutions.
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- FAQ 3 -->
                <div class="border border-white/5 rounded-xl overflow-hidden bg-slate-900">
                    <button @click="open = open === 2 ? null : 2"
                            class="w-full flex items-center justify-between p-6 text-left gap-4"
                            id="faq-btn-2">
                        <span class="font-semibold text-white">Do you work with clients outside the US?</span>
                        <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-slate-800 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 transition-transform duration-200"
                               :class="open === 2 ? 'rotate-45 bg-brand-500' : ''">
                            <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M12 4v16m8-8H4"></path></svg>
                        </span>
                    </button>
                    <div x-show="open === 2"
                         x-transition:enter="transition ease-out duration-200"
                         x-transition:enter-start="opacity-0 -translate-y-2"
                         x-transition:enter-end="opacity-100 translate-y-0"
                         class="px-6 pb-6 text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed border-t border-white/5 pt-4" style="display:none;">
                        Absolutely. We work with clients across North America, Europe, and the Middle East. Our remote-first workflow ensures seamless collaboration regardless of timezone.
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- FAQ 4 -->
                <div class="border border-white/5 rounded-xl overflow-hidden bg-slate-900">
                    <button @click="open = open === 3 ? null : 3"
                            class="w-full flex items-center justify-between p-6 text-left gap-4"
                            id="faq-btn-3">
                        <span class="font-semibold text-white">What happens after launch?</span>
                        <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-slate-800 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 transition-transform duration-200"
                               :class="open === 3 ? 'rotate-45 bg-brand-500' : ''">
                            <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M12 4v16m8-8H4"></path></svg>
                        </span>
                    </button>
                    <div x-show="open === 3"
                         x-transition:enter="transition ease-out duration-200"
                         x-transition:enter-start="opacity-0 -translate-y-2"
                         x-transition:enter-end="opacity-100 translate-y-0"
                         class="px-6 pb-6 text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed border-t border-white/5 pt-4" style="display:none;">
                        We offer ongoing retainer packages for maintenance, optimization, and growth. Many of our clients have been with us for 3+ years because we become a true extension of their team.
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- FAQ 5 -->
                <div class="border border-white/5 rounded-xl overflow-hidden bg-slate-900">
                    <button @click="open = open === 4 ? null : 4"
                            class="w-full flex items-center justify-between p-6 text-left gap-4"
                            id="faq-btn-4">
                        <span class="font-semibold text-white">Can you redesign an existing website?</span>
                        <span class="w-6 h-6 rounded-full bg-slate-800 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 transition-transform duration-200"
                               :class="open === 4 ? 'rotate-45 bg-brand-500' : ''">
                            <svg class="w-3 h-3 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2.5" d="M12 4v16m8-8H4"></path></svg>
                        </span>
                    </button>
                    <div x-show="open === 4"
                         x-transition:enter="transition ease-out duration-200"
                         x-transition:enter-start="opacity-0 -translate-y-2"
                         x-transition:enter-end="opacity-100 translate-y-0"
                         class="px-6 pb-6 text-slate-400 text-sm leading-relaxed border-t border-white/5 pt-4" style="display:none;">
                        Yes — redesigns are one of our specialties. We audit your existing site, identify opportunities, and deliver a modernized experience that retains SEO equity while dramatically improving performance.
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</Layout>
